# Scheduling events for Solarfertigation


### Prerequisites
1. Install [Node.js](https://nodejs.org)
2. `git clone https://solarfertigation.visualstudio.com/Raspi_code/_git/Raspi_code`
3. From project root folder install all the package.json dependencies: 
```
npm i
```
 
- In case of compiling failure of `sqlite3`, specify 

```
npm install sqlite3 --build-from-source
```

and then 

```
CXX=clang++ npm i
```

### Notes
- `onoff` package only for raspberry pi system


